GRAB A SLICE
Celebrate Old School RuneScape’s 1st Anniversary on Mobile by grabbing a slice of cake from the Varrock fountains on the 31st October.

BRAND NEW GAME MODE
Play our brand new time-limited game mode Twisted League! You’ll have two months to earn exclusive rewards for the Main Game. Complete Kourend and Kebos's biggest challenges and use powerful Relics to upgrade your experience!

Thrilling New Quest:
Unlock the coveted city of Prifddinas by completing the Song of the Elves quest and revealing the final mysteries that lie within the Elven storyline.

Exciting New Minigame:
Enter the Gauntlet, and defeat the Crystall
• Minor bug fixes and optimisations.

• Updated store listing screenshots.
• Minor bug fixes.

• Enhanced performance and memory usage of the world map.
• Ice and lava abyssal whips should now display properly on mobile devices.
• The world switcher now handles large amounts of worlds more gracefully.

• Explore the Kebos Lowlands, the largest Gielinor map expansion.
• Battle through the new slayer dungeon, where undiscovered monsters dwell.
• Discover the farming guild, a new place for budding farmers to thrive.
• Uncover the secrets from TWO
